### 1. 注册新学生
POST http://localhost:8085/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "student_security_01",
  "password": "123456",
  "realName": "安全测试学生",
  "role": "STUDENT"
}

### 2. 登录成功
POST http://localhost:8085/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "student_security_01",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 3. 登录失败：密码错误
POST http://localhost:8085/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "student_security_01",
  "password": "wrong_password"
}

### 4. 登录失败：用户不存在
POST http://localhost:8085/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "not_exist_user",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 5. 注册失败：用户名重复
POST http://localhost:8085/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "student_security_01",
  "password": "123456",
  "realName": "重复用户",
  "role": "STUDENT"
}